                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6489" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1650</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8888 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">瑞牛文创：陶瓷文创产品规模化定制探索之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Renew: The exploration of large-scale customization of ceramic cultural and creative products</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘冰峰，李婧，欧阳桃花，龚克（通讯作者），韩静，陈莎莉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">景德镇陶瓷大学*</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">瑞牛文化科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值链重构；传统文创产业；区域产业转型升级；陶瓷文创产品；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Value chain reconstruction; Traditional cultural and creative industries;Regional industrial transformation and upgrading; Ceramic cultural and creative products </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生活陶瓷是日用消费品，也是文化创意产品。景德镇形成的手工制瓷工艺体系，曾创造中国陶瓷史的传奇。而当今，景德镇陶瓷产业却面临难以对接工业大规模生产文明的迷局。个性化易，规模化难。这不仅是景德镇上万家陶瓷文创企业的困惑，也是众多中国传统文创企业面临的挑战。瑞牛文化科技有限公司（以下简称：瑞牛文创）成立于2019年2月，面对产业痛点，探索陶瓷文创产品走向产业化的路径。瑞牛文创以为B端客户提供规模定制服务为价值定位，重构价值链，以设计与研发为引领，整合供应链资源，为客户提供既有个性化又可规模化制造的陶瓷文创定制服务与产品。2022年，瑞牛文创步入规模以上企业行列，荣获国家级版权示范单位。如何将新时代的需求融于有着悠久历史文化的陶瓷文创产品，创造出更广阔的市场？瑞牛文创在持续探索中。本案例有助于读者理解价值链重构理论在新情境下的新应用与新内涵。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Living ceramics are daily consumer goods and cultural and creative products. The handmade porcelain craft system formed in Jingdezhen has created a legend in the history of Chinese ceramics. Today, Jingdezhen’s ceramic industry is facing the difficulty of connecting with industrial mass production civilization. Personalization is easy, scale is difficult. This is not only the confusion of tens of thousands of ceramic cultural and creative enterprises in Jingdezhen, but also the challenge faced by many traditional Chinese cultural and creative enterprises. Renew was established in February 2019, facing the pain points of the industry, exploring the path of ceramic cultural and creative products to industrialization. Renew takes the value proposition of providing large-scale customization services for B-end customers, reconstructs the value chain, takes design and R&amp;D as the guide, integrates supply chain resources, and provides customers with both personalized and large-scale manufacturing of ceramic cultural and creative customized services and products. In 2022, Renew will enter the ranks of enterprises above designated size and won the national copyright demonstration unit. How to integrate the needs of the new era into ceramic cultural and creative products with a long history and culture to create a broader market? Renew is in continuous exploration. This case helps readers to understand the new application and new connotation of the value chain reconstruction theory in the new situation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">特定产业价值链待征；价值定位的策略及风险；价值链重构的方法及难点；价值链重构的价值创造与增长逻辑</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
